@startuml
actor User
boundary CommentView
control CommentController
entity COMMENT

User -> CommentView : Select function reply comment
activate CommentView
User -> CommentView : Enter reply detail
User -> CommentView : Click button "Reply"
CommentView -> CommentView : Validate input information

alt Valid input
    CommentView -> CommentController : replyComment(parentId, data)
    activate CommentController
    CommentController -> COMMENT : Validate reply data
    activate COMMENT

    alt Valid data
        COMMENT --> CommentController : Validation success
        CommentController -> COMMENT : Store reply
        COMMENT --> CommentController : Reply created
        CommentController --> CommentView : Success response
        CommentView --> User : Notify reply success
        User -> CommentView : Confirm success notification
    else Invalid data
        COMMENT --> CommentController : Validation error
        CommentController --> CommentView : Error response
        CommentView --> User : Notify invalid data
        User -> CommentView : Confirm error notification
    end
    deactivate COMMENT
    deactivate CommentController
else Invalid input
    CommentView --> User : Notify invalid input
    User -> CommentView : Confirm error notification
end
deactivate CommentView
@enduml